                        <li><a href="/web/20180712203504/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_Age_of_Target_Population=Child%20%282%20to%2012%20years%29&amp;fLockTerm=Child%2B%282%2Bto%2B12%2Byears%29">Child (2 to 12 years)</a></li>                      
            </ul>
                    <h4>UMLS Concepts <a href="/web/20180712203504/https://www.guideline.gov/help-and-about/search-browse/umls-concepts" class="what-is">(what is this?)</a></h4>
