            <p><a class="" target="" href="/web/20180712203504/https://www.guideline.gov/summaries/summary/51300/mental-health-care-in-the-perinatal-period-australian-clinical-practice-guideline">Mental health care in the perinatal period: Australian clinical practice guideline.</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="list-item-small">
        <ul class="item-meta">
            <li> NGC:011372</li>
            <li>2015</li>
        </ul>
       
            <p><a class="" target="" href="/web/20180712203504/https://www.guideline.gov/summaries/summary/51294/clinical-practice-guideline-on-systemic-lupus-erythematosus">Clinical practice guideline on systemic lupus erythematosus.</a></p>
    </div>
